Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.54,0:01:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no Shakespeare line,{シェイクスピアではないけれど}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but our High Collar Lady can't decide between staying and leaving.{とどまるべきかかるべきかそれが問題のhaikaraさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.14,0:01:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The egoistical Ranmaru and Ushigorou{人の気も知らない蘭丸とushigorou}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,got fired up and started their offensive,{張り切って攻撃を開始して}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,which managed to drive\Nthe hard-working Kisaragi crazy.{しごきの名人きさらぎもついにダウンの気の毒者}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.19,0:01:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu seems to have unmasked Ranmaru,{だがしかしshouiは蘭丸の正体を}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.12,0:01:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but for some reason he keeps playing dumb.{知っているのに知らない総理}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Our High Collar Lady can't understand Shinobu's deepest feelings{そんなshouiの心の底を測りかねたるはいからさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is just confusing and hurting her.{思い乱れるばかりなり}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! It's my turn this morning!{ダメ！今朝はあたし！}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:01:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Never! I'll be doing it!{ないよ私が磨くの}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:02:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my duty to take care of Young Master!{若様の身の回りは全部あたしが！}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So leave it to me!{では若様は}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you both want to clean so bad, how about doing it together?{そんなに磨きたいんだったら仲良く片方ずつやったらどう}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it could definitely work.{なんでそうすればいいんだわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.49,0:02:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.{おはようございます}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at this! Mine is tidier!{ねぇ見て見て私の方が綺麗よ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Lies! Mine is sparkling!{嘘、私の方がぴかぴかよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true at all!{そんなことないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, shouldn't you be the one taking care of Shinobu?{benioさん, shouiの身の回りのことを人任せにしていいのねぇ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Benio, are you listening?{ねえ紅緒さんってば}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have to look after him{あんな人の世話をするくらいなら}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather treat him this way!{こっちの方はよっぽどマシよ - I don't understand if that 方 is meant this way or is referred to something such as ""}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel!{わかるわかるその気持ち}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good attitude!{いい傾向ね}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That sublieutenant doesn't care about me at all...{私のこと何とも思っていないshouiなんか}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:03:01.26,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\c&HF1E6E4&\pos(467.027,66.667)\bord0\blur0.667\fs60\b1}Episode 14\NTwo blooming admirers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.94,0:03:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't worry!{ご心配ごめんよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll reassemble it right now!{すぐ組み立てますから}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a foot, I think...{これが足}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio! You should rather take care of Young Master at least a bit!{Benio-sama!少しは若様の身の回りをお世話して差し上げなければ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about him...{誰が少尉なんか}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, it's fine.{いいよいいよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll do it myself.{では私が代わりに}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master, here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Today you don't have your pads on your back anymore, good job, good job!{今朝はパットが背中に回っていないね結構結構}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mercy is worthy of a samurai!{武士の情け肝に銘じてありがたく}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, where are my gloves?{手袋は}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, such disregard!{もう何たる(?)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone, please bring the gloves here!{これ誰か急ぎ取ってきなさいはい}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait, though.{あ待ちなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure did it fast!{はやっとできた}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?{なんかおっしゃった}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}your{\i0} job!{あなたのお仕事です}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring Young Master's gloves here once and for all!{すぐ若様の手袋をお取りしてきなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you do it yourself?{取ってくればいいんでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This one?{これだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!{そうだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how he'd react{右手ばっかり持ってったら}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,if I gave him two right hand ones!{どんな顔するかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She is rather late. Why is it taking so long?{遅いわね何してるのかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to have kept you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.{では}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please return soon, Young Master!{いってらっしゃいませ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How boring...{なんだつまんない}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He went away without putting them on.{手袋はめないで行っちゃった}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it about?{それどういうこと}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like making fun of Shinobu,{からかってやろうと思って}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so I gave him two right hand gloves!{手袋右手だけ2つ持たせてやったのほら左手は}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, the left ones.{ほら左手はここ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Brilliant as usual!{やるんさすが}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, that could turn out even better!{親分それちょいとした事件になりやすぜ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If I recall correctly, Shinobu should be a standard-bearer.{伊集院少尉は確か連隊旗手だったんじゃねえんですかい}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, my father once mentioned this.{そういえばお父様が以前そんなことおっしゃってたわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's a standard-bearer?{ねぇねぇ連隊旗手って何}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute his Majesty the Emperor.{賢くも天皇陛下から賜った}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,At ease.{休め}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He holds the national flag!{軍旗を持つ役目でよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.07,0:06:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute the flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In the regiment, only the most qualified officers{その連隊で一番優秀な青年将校が}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,can become standard-bearers.{目を張る旗手になるの}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And to do that, it is necessary to wear white gloves.{ちゃんと白い手袋をはめなきゃ旗手は止まらぬ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then if someone forgets his gloves...{じゃあ手袋を忘れたとなれば}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly what you're thinking!{まず間違いなく}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.30,0:06:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll get a good scolding by the commander{師団長から大目玉を喰らうし}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And since your father is Shinobu's direct superior,{親分のお父上も少尉の直属上官として}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.43,0:06:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll face the consequences too.{絞られることは決定的でさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.44,0:06:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This much trouble?{そんな大騒ぎになるの}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's all settled!{まずバッチリと決まりだなぁ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This way Benio will 100% be kicked out!{これで間違いなく微妙さんはオン出される}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.91,0:06:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hip hip, hooray! Hip hip, hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do?{どうしようどうしよう}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, I didn't think it'd go this way!{shouiそんなつもりじゃなかったのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.93,0:07:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!{ごめんね}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Get outta my way! Go-go-go-go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, what's wrong? You've been quite gloomy!{親分どうしたんださっきから(?)ばかりで}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.{何でもないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The glove matter should have had an effect by now.{もう手袋事件の結果が出てる頃だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This way you'll be able to say goodbye to that mansion, right, Boss?{これであのお屋敷ともおさらばですぜ親分}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you stop all of a sudden?{何を急に止まったりして}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hehe...{dunno what he's saying}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.49,0:07:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are those guys?{何をこの人たち}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey hey hey!{いやいやいやい}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a public road, so get outta my way!{ここは天下の往来だどいてもらううちはねえかよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me what to do!{わめくんじゃねえ - not sure about what he's saying...}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the lady who got engaged with the sublieutenant Ijuuin, right?{伊集院少尉と婚約したっていうのはお姉さんだな}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We are...{あしらは}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the most influent gang{関東一円に}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in the whole Kanto district!{縄張りをもつやくざ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Say our name out loud,{その名も高き}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet squad!{すみれ組 - sumire squad}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet squad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, stop! Ushigorou, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so then you guys must love{はいそれじゃああんたたちは}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,singing the violet song!{すみれ組のさんしただから - not really sure, don't know what sanshita is supposed to mean}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we surely do!{そうさんしたすみれなの}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A violet flower...{すみれの花}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A violet flower{ this song https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_R5j5zkneRg}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,started blooming{咲く頃}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the time I met you-{初めて君を...}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! This is not the time to sing!{歌ってるばやいかよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing!{笑うじゃねぇ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't hold any grudge against you, but I gotta do what I gotta do,{アンさんには恨みつらみはござんせんが渡世の義理}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.88,0:09:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'll have to hurt you a bit.{ちっとばかり痛い目にあっていただきやす}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!? What do you mean by that!?{なんですってどういうわけで}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No arguing, get off!{問答無用降りよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna pick a fight, then?{私に降りろとおっしゃるの}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you've got it.{耳がありゃ聞こえたろ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept your challenge,{私をどうしたりしたら - not sure}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but know that I won't take any responsibility.{どんなことになるか責任持てないわよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, don't overvalue yourself,{聞いたくなくちゃだけじゃねえか}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and bring it on!{野郎め}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, it's looking bad,{親分,相手が悪い}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,these guys rule the streets.{こいつらはその道のプロで}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So what of it?{それがどうしたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a great chance to boost my mood today!{こっちは今日はちょっとばかり虫の居所が悪いんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! I'll be facing you!{よし俺が相手だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You-!{やろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep in mind that you started all of this!{喧嘩売ったのはそっちだってこと覚えといてね}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Don't mess with me!{何これでも}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go!{やった}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,One down! Now you, attack me from wherever!{さあどっからでもかかっといて}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This whore! I went easy on her 'cause she's a woman!{このあま女だと思って手加減してやったら}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to get serious!{勘弁ならねぇ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bitch!{めろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready!{?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine, Ushigoro.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know why, but it's been a while and I'm excited!{なんだかわかんないけど久しぶりではワクワクしちゃう}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Rot in...{地獄へ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,hell!{落ちろ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Get spanked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are cheeky!{しゃらくせえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.91,0:10:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,En garde!{覚悟}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:10:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally.{やっぱり}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Straight to hell.{地獄行き}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to die!{死んでもらいや}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna kill me like yakuzas?{あんたたちヤクザのクズに}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.74,0:11:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then try to do it!{やられてたまるもんですか - I don't really know what she's supposed to be saying - the trasliteration should be right though}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!{おやめ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Kichiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is wrong with you?{お前さんたちなんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Going three against one!{たった一人大勢で}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But we were concerned about you...{しかしあしらは姉さんの気持ちを}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Such things are unasked for!{余計なことをお呼びでないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember ever promising to pay you for anything.{私はお前たちなんかに払いする頼んだ覚えはないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a word more!{おだまり}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She's pretty. And also so strong-willed!{美人！それにすんごい迫力}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologise, Young Lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,for what these guys have put you through.{知り合いのものが飛んだごぶれいをしまして}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a geisha from Yanagibashi,{わたくし、柳橋の芸者}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,my name is Hananoya Kichiji.{花の屋吉二と申しますお}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So you are Ms. Kichiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And this lady is Hanamura Benio?{嬢さんはhanamura benio様}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.40,0:12:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know me, though?{でもどうして私のことを}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I happen to be in...{この吉次はね伊集院の若様に}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,To be in?{若様に}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In love with Young Master.{惚れておりましたのさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it's one-sided{もちろん片思いですけどね}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and now I'm completely sure that I can't do anything{でもいくらこちらが熱をあげてもかなわないはず}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,if you are his fiancée.{こんなお嬢様が許嫁なら}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's not like that. A-Actually we...{あら違います私たち}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't officially married yet,{まだ婚約なんて正式じゃないし}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.47,0:13:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,also Shinobu doesn't really...{それにSHOUIは私のことなんか}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?{何をおっしゃいます}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It is plain to see.{お嬢様を一目見ればわかります}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I could never be chosen.{それに引き換え私なぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:13:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A noble with a geisha like me{家族様と芸者風情}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,would be together only in my wildest dreams.{結ばれるなんて夢のまた夢}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I even started{でもできることなら}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to think to break your engagement{婚約をぶち壊してやりたい}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.77,0:14:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in every way possible.{とまで思っていました}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,After meeting you today,{今日測らずも(?)}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I understood that I can't compare.{こうしてお嬢様にお会いするまではね}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady.{お嬢様}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Take good care of Young Master!{若さもよろしくお頼みしましたよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Kichiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, that shameless womaniser!{まああの女性の敵}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fooling that geisha and doing such things behind my back!{少尉のやつあの芸者さんと陰で(適当?)にやってたのね}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just the worst! I'll never forgive him!{許せないたんじて赦せない}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That hypocrite!{?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even have a cold though...{風でもないのにくしゃみが一つ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Ijuuin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did anything happen to Young Lady for you to be here?{振り残した何事かお嬢様の身の上に起こったんでございますか}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't want to upset you, so I won't say anything.{まぁね 怒らないといえば嘘になりますが}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good grief,{あーもうダメだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to think that it was such a great engagement!{せっかくのいいご縁談だったのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't ever forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.{おかえりなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, what's wrong?{紅生さんどうしたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru, today's the day to pack my things and leave.{Ranmaru,今日っていう今日は荷物をまとめてちょうだい}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already done that in foresight.{そう来ると思ってもうまとめてあるわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? Are you a clairvoyant?{えっあんた千里眼なの}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's about you, I can make my telepathy work!{紅緒さんに関することならテレパシーが働いちゃうの}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just joking. Anyways, I'll bring your things here.{それは冗談だけどじゃあ荷物取ってくる}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.57,0:16:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?{何をそれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell? It's today's share of love letters{決まってるでしょshouiのところへ来るラブレター}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,directed to Shinobu.{本日の分}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like this everyday!{毎日これだもんね}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen such a playboy before!{あんなプレイボーイ見たことないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the author!? Really?{原作者お前もか}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:22.27,Sign,,0,0,0,,Shinobu-san\NI'm head over heels for you{seems like mairu to me, though I'm unsure} \N♥Waki{it's the manga author's name - https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Waki_Yamato ; another reading is "Kazunori"}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of this!{もう完全に頭に来た}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.71,0:16:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He's late, isn't he?{遅いなもう}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here, shall we go now?{行きましょうよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,One second.{待って}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to tell Shinobu just one thing before we leave.{一つだけ勝利に聞きたいことがあるの}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Do you still have feelings for him?{あらまだあんな男に未練があるの}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that, it's just one quick thing.{そうじゃないわ一言ガンって言ってやるのそう}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then.{そうガーンとね}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You got into trouble because of the gloves, right?{手袋のことお困りになったでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she doing!?{どうなってんのこれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.87,0:17:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Leutenant, that was very inconsiderate of me.{少尉あれは私が悪いんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I put many people in trouble, didn't I?{大勢の人にご迷惑がかかったんじゃないんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I just found it funny!{あれには笑っちゃいましたよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thankfully, this world is full of scatterbrains and today{いや世の中にはあわてものがいるもんで}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,another officer coincidentally brought two left-handed gloves.{今日偶然左手だけを2つ持ってきた将校がいましてね}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So I exchanged my right glove with his left one{僕はその人と右と左を片方ずつ取り替えて}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and we made it through alright.{結局2人とも何事もなし}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,can you guess who this officer{その左手だけを持ってきた将校というのが}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,actually was?{誰だと思います}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,None other than your father!{benioさんのお父上の花村少佐}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.01,0:17:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It is probably because{ということは バーヤの不注意で}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of a careless mistake by Nanny.{バーヤがぼんやりしていたからです}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanny...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since you left her, she must've been feeling lonely{バーヤは紅緒さんがいなくなって\Nきっと寂しい思いをしてるんですね}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,without a moment of relief.{だから心が虚ろなんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hence she made this mistake.{だからミスをするんですね}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanny...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So I,{それで僕}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,on the way back,{帰りがけに}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,decided to console her a bit.{ばあやを慰めにさっきお邪魔をしてきました}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Such self-aggrandisement,{そんな親切ごかしを言ったって}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand him!{騙されはしないと}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know modesty,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,this shamless womaniser!{(寝たなあかてんだか?) - dunno}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanny gave something for you two.{バヤさんに頼まれてきたものがあります}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this is for you.{こちらははい}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru- err, Ranko.{蘭丸じゃない蘭子さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,These sure are{すごい数だね}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of love letters.{みんなラブレター}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really happy about it,{冗談でしょファンレターよ (?)}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I get all these letters despite not having any feelings for them.{こっちは何とも思ってないのに勝手によこすんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just dull.{本当にやんなっちゃう}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel you,{わかるわかる}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like this everyday for me.{僕のところへも毎日来るんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know who's sending them,{こっちは全然預かり知らないのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.07,0:19:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,it's all one-sided.{一方的にね}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,One-sided?{一方的に}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so pretentious!{気取っちゃって}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And these are for Benio, one from Nanny.{これは何をさえ1つはバーヤさんから}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sabu and Hiroshi.{あーサブちゃんとひろしくん}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they?{何者です}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Two kids in my neighbourhood.{近所の小学生なるほど}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect them to write me a letter.{あの子たちが手紙をよこすなんて}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Benio, let's climb trees and play again sometime!{はいけい紅緒さんまた木登りして遊ぼうよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Crimbing trees?{木登り}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Hiroshi?{ひろしくんは}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, when are you coming back?{紅緒さんいつ帰るの}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.53,0:19:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna climb a tree!{早くキノボリがしたいね}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget when we climbed one back then!{僕いつもbenioさんと木登りしたことを忘れないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hiroshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? It's all about treeclimbing!{何をこれ木登りばっかじゃないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm not popular after all!{私のところはこんな色っぽくない}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No love letters at all!{ファンレターばっか}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:54.24,Sign,,0,0,0,,To Benio-san \N- Hiroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about these!{どこへでもとんでけ(?)}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Laugh as you please!{なんと笑いなさいよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my bad.{いや失礼}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna keep on laughing forever?{いつまでも笑ってるといいわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know your secrets!{少尉のメッキはもうハゲているんですからね}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.17,0:20:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Like your beloved Ms. Kichiji, huh?{花のやの吉じ姉さんがよろしくですすって}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You met her?{彼女に会ったんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your expression changed!{顔色が変わった}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...{彼女は}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,wrong on her matter, Benio.{違いますそんな}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.10,0:20:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't misunderstand.{誤解しないでください}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need lame excuses.{言い訳は見苦しいわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate people like you who play with women's feelings,{あなたのように女の気持ちを持って遊ぶ人大っ嫌い}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Out, out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,After all,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what,{どうせどうせ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.65,0:21:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a nominal fiancée.{私は名義上だけの許婚}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just fated to a loveless forced marriage.{いくら親の決めたラブぬき結婚だって}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too much to bear!{これじゃあんまりひどすぎる}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a sad fate for a woman{妻とはいえどうわべだけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,to stay with an unfaithful man{夫の浮気はなきねいり}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.43,0:21:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,with no chance of divorcing{さりとて離婚は許されず}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and being completely overwhelmed by housework.{わが身粉にして働いて哀れ儚く消えてゆく}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.48,0:21:30.14,Sign,,0,0,0,,Why do we have so many children?{なぜか子供だけはたくさんいる}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.16,0:21:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It should never happen.{女の悲しき運命よ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.59,0:21:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of this!{やっぱりやめた}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.95,0:21:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just leave!{こんなうちおんでってやる}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.00,0:21:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:39.11,Sign,,0,0,0,,To Young Lady{お嬢さまへ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter from Nanny?{バーヤの手紙}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Young Lady, how are you?{\i0}{お嬢様お元気ですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As for me, I am living peacefully all alone with your father.{\i0}{私は旦那様と二人っきりでのんびりしています}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.88,0:21:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He has never been worried about you,{\i0}{お嬢様のことを思い出すことなど一度もありませんどう}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.55,0:21:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so, whatever happens,\Nplease never consider returning home.{\i0}{どうかくれぐれも二度と家へ帰るなんて気持ちおこさないでください}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.92,0:22:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Moreover, I have never had the wish to see your face again,{\i0}{私はお嬢様の顔を見たいなんて一度も思ったことはないんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.48,0:22:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so I beg you not to ever come back home.{\i0}{お願いですから何があっても家だけには戻らないでください}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Never, never come back home, please.{\i0}{決して 決して戻らないでください}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.28,0:22:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Never,{\i0}{決して}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}never come back home, please.{\i0}{決して戻らないでください}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanny...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.51,0:22:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,After all,{人の世は}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.67,0:22:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,people always have two sides,{裏と表の使い分け}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.25,0:22:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anything you can do to untie the thread in your tormented heart, try it out{知事に乱れた心の糸を解けるものならほぐしてごらん}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.52,0:22:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and a flower will bloom.{解けたら咲きます}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.74,0:22:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Which will it be?{何の花}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.88,0:22:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,During the airing of old family possessions,{伊集院家の古い品物の虫干しで}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.16,0:23:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,something slips from Ranmaru's hand and breaks{蘭丸が手を滑らせてポロリと割った皿1枚}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.50,0:23:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and oh goodness, it was a precious plate!{なんとこれが大事な果報のお皿}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The count obviously snaps out and unsheathes his katana,{怒り狂った老伯爵は成敗出すと刀を抜いた}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.87,0:23:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and, to give all plates the same fate,{ならば残り9人分の身代わりと - not sure}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.69,0:23:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio decides to break all of them! Big trouble!{紅葉がお皿全部を叩き割ったからさ大変}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.69,0:23:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on "Here Comes the Smart Alec":
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So long, old-fashioned mansion. Don't miss it!{さようなら、古きものよ！お楽しみに}
